STEP 1
Objective: Installation and Understand basic webpack configuration using basic flags to modify generated code.

INSTALLING YARN

1 - Run "npm install -g yarn" or Download the installer
2 - Install yarn
4 - Verify  "yarn --version"
5 - Run "yarn init"

